item.title: Browser Caching with htaccess
item.description: Browser caching is a good idea to make/feel your site speedy . Your sites visitors will find it much speedier after first visit . If you test your page in pingdom and google speed analysis tool you will see a recommendation there to enable caching . That is why i am sharing this .
